Naslednjo iteracijo zapišite z zanko while: 
Pascal: 
C: 
for x:='A' to 'F' do begin 
for (x='A';x<='F';x++) { 
  writeln (pred(x),' ',succ(x)); 
  printf("%c %c\n",x-1,x+1); 
  writeln(x:2); 
  printf("%2c\n",x); 
end; 
} 
